trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyInfo"></xref> objects.
This class cannot be inherited.
The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyCollection> class does not refer to any actual element in the underlying configuration file.
It is a construct that allows access to the assembly information it contains.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyCollection"></xref> class.
Adds an <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyInfo"></xref> object to the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyCollection"></xref> collection.
Adds an <xref:System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyInfo> object to the collection.
If the assembly object is not initialized with assembly information, an exception is thrown.
If the assembly object already exists in the collection, the statement is ignored.
A string value specifying the assembly reference.
Clears all the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyInfo"></xref> objects from the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyCollection"></xref> collection.
Gets or sets the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyInfo"></xref> at the specified index in the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyCollection"></xref>.
An integer value specifying a specific <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyInfo"></xref> object within the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyCollection"></xref> collection.
A <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyInfo"></xref> object.
Gets the item identified by the specified assembly name.
The name identifying the assembly to retrieve.
The item identified by the specified assembly name.
Removes a <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyInfo"></xref> object from the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyCollection"></xref> collection.
If the assembly does not exist in the collection, the statement is ignored.
A string value specifying the assembly reference.
Removes an <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyInfo"></xref> object from the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyCollection"></xref> collection.
If the assembly does not exist in the collection, an out-of-range exception is thrown.
An integer value specifying an <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyInfo"></xref> object within the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyCollection"></xref> collection.
